Description: nvtop-style NVIDIA GPU monitor with NVLink visibility
  1CatLinkStat is a real-time terminal GPU monitor for NVIDIA systems.
  It reports GPU utilization, memory, clocks, power, PCIe activity,
  active NVLink channel count, configured NVLink bandwidth, and real
  NVLink RX/TX totals through DCGM when supported by the platform.
